Comment: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{this line is too long}{\an8}With the body of an adult, the heart of a child, lovely whiskers, and a gentleman's demeanor, I'm Mr. Experiment.
Comment: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello, everybody. Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm the gentleman you've known forever, Mr. Experiment!
Comment: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In this corner, let's try to solve mysteries found in your everyday lives!
Comment: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{13:39 TS}Tatsumi Textiles

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, but my master is out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I see you've helped your new bonds blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon and Strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how these two Arcana will influence your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back again when my master has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you prefer it when he's away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.20,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Glaciers of ideas, importing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.40,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To my friends, then exporting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To the next, keeping it open
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:57.87,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We want no closing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Even without those, our thoughts can be duped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}This mind trade no one can stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}An act of thinking is terrible to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We just wanna change it up, not drop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}And my crew can rock it like uprock{APPARENTLY A REAL THING: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uprock}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:09.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Life is tedious if it ain't flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:11.05,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Copy and paste? Constant defaulting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:11.84,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Put my courage to it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.67,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Begin showing off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:13.80,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}That's the way we wanna live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:14.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep going, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:18.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}What was so much of transparency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:22.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Turned into bright expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:29.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Instinct tells me to keep going together, going together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:36.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}It's breathtaking moments in life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:43.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Addicted to it, minds craving more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.37,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}I'm believing you and I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.30,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We can change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:56.42,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}The sky's the limit, we can spread wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:03.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}to roadless travel, together we go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about the new first-year student?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did! But is it for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how he beat up an entire biker gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 1 versus 100, and he just about beat 'em to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bastard!{kanji}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took over the biker gang and became their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some TV station is even sending someone to interview him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Take that!{kanji}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a degenerate like him doing in our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next, we'll cover the case on everyone's mind, Ms. Yamano's murder.{tv}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this fried chicken good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Although singer Hiiragi Misuzu is a suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}her alibi has been confirmed. She was on tour abroad on the day of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Yep, we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The man she had the affair with, Namatame Taro, also has a solid alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ms. Yamano had only recently returned to her hometown of Inaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And Namatame had witnesses confirm that he was doing office work all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I have to work late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to lock the door and hit the hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About me taking off the 4th and the 5th...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the younger guys got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His case doesn't look like it can be put on hold,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm stuck filling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to take a hard-earned break during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the sudden change in plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you could look after Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The police are currently investigating the connection between the high school student and Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're free today, wanna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko's coming too, and we can invite Hanamura if we really have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, wanna come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Here's one steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Nanako. Eat up and enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to chew a lot. This isn't quality steak or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! How could you say that right in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But geez, what are you doing wasting Golden Week here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere else to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, don't you feel sorry for Nanako, since you brought her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come see for yourself, and get in touch with our products!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to rub it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day's great at your Junes!{nanako + tv}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were supposed to bring our own lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You know how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what, are you a great cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just do it for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're the family cook? Pretty impressive, "Big Bro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, that's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got Satonaka beat hands down.{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think I can't cook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I challenge you to a cook-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Nanako can be our judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I competing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we'll make something that ranks up there with your mom's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't have a mom, I have Dad with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now a big brother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm having a lot of fun today! I love Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, we'll play with you anytime you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thanks for tuning in, all you curious kiddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I broke my promise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. My big bro played with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, today's Children's Day, so I bought you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a weird thing on the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you're still a child or anything, but fair's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This swimsuit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,very fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Big Bro, let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we last ate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! It sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to eat before the steak gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura insisted on forming a study group,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there weren't any incidents during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now? You wanna talk about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, he came back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually put some thought into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first victim was Ms. Yamano, followed by Konishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Amagi was the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't picked out at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's some sort of motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A motive? But there's no connection between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. All three victims were connected in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Konishi was the one who found Ms. Yamano's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And didn't Ms. Yamano stay at the Amagi Inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't this be a fair assumption?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women associated with Ms. Yamano are being targeted one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll never get anywhere if we don't piece together the few clues we {\i1}do{\i0} have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall the doorbell ringing and someone calling for me, but not who.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, there's the Midnight Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, it might be warning us who's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we have to check the Midnight Channel every night it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Then we can prevent anything from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now that we're all on the same page, let's call it a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get even a minute of studying done.
