Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, free at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd get the same grade whether or not I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be that carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A biker gang composed of young men terrorize this quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ambitious enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadduya want?{kanji on tv}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Their alleged boss suddenly attacked the cameraman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't a freak show, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still pulling this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, through work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Tatsumi Kanji, a troubled teen who loves getting into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{12:22 eyectach, top-most and clockwise}
