Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby commence the Special Investigation Team meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,690,640,712)\t(\fs45)}We hereby commence the Special Investigation Team meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}for the Inaba serial murders and kidnappings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}Too long.{that's what she said}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}So this is our secret headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}You got it! Amagi, you're on the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}Anyway, about the guy on the Midnight Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}You mean Tatsumi Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}We just saw him on the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}Man, we missed the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}So much for the victims only being women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}I doubt there's any connection between Ms. Yamano and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,712)\fs45}Kanji, huh? He wasn't like this when he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, you actually know that creep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His family runs a textile shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inn has sold their wares for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't spoken with Kanji for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That simplifies things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check out that textile shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. If the people on the Midnight Channel are being thrown into the TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi Kanji will be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Come on in, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry I wasn't much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. You gave me something to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, you're as beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this scarf somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was there, in the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the room with the faceless posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Ms. Yamano's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you friends with Ms. Yamano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a special order she placed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Package delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I have to step out for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We were just leaving, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tatsumi Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You want to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm quite interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you after school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's "interested"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a guy, and I'm a guy, but he's interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you pricks looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's their problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear a word they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's keep watch over Tatsumi Kanji and the textile shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. If the killer really is after Tatsumi Kanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll either approach him directly or drop by his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, Amagi, can I have your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you were after!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! But I'll be needing it for stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, could you stop calling me at night to tell me dirty jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Amagi. You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that I have to get some tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about them seems weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Maybe it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Satonaka and I will trail Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami and Amagi, keep an eye on Tatsumi Textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{17:16}Tatsumi Textiles
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the killer will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little, but my desire to see this through outweights it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's something I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stress about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ease up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a chance the killer won't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. I'm nervous about something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been alone with a boy my age before or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, of course, has no problem with guys because of her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Tatsuhime Shrine}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she's had more fun hanging out with you and Hanamura lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same is true for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I made things even more awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Chie's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the line's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know Hanamura's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura's number?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might need it for the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. We need to keep in contact with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I cut to the chase and ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, Satonaka, do you copy? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is conversing 200 meters in front of me. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we positioned like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd both get busted if he found us together. Over, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put "over" in the wrong spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking we should split up a little. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100% guaranteed he'd get us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I'm getting hungry. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care! Why don't you just order delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delivery? But we're outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiya's known to deliver anywhere and everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'd like a delivery for two beef bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said one's for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadduya think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're just a loving couple passing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't argue with me, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not going along with that story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Didn't I see you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't trying to get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't think it's strange or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, you moron! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! I swear it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we brought trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's chasing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead! You're so friggin' dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! He's gonna get all of us at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to become our decoy, Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the line, "I'll handle him. You keep going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, don’t let him trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to stop running from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you find us when we've been on the move?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The total is 1,600 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blow me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Do you have change?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're paying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, here's a hundred yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's so nice and warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this sucks! We can't keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's disband already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get kidnapped without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep an eye on him a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I leave the bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED Placeholder}
