Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, dear viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll introduce a superb site for those searching for a sublime love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that surpasses the separation of the sexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.34,0:24:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be your host.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tatsumi Kanji, my darlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold it! It's too gay in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop this shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for one last hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Change!
